Alias       myD*-       D*-
Alias       myD*+       D*+
ChargeConj  myD*+       myD*-
Alias myD0 D0
Alias myanti-D0 anti-D0
ChargeConj myD0 myanti-D0
Alias myK_S0 K_S0
ChargeConj myK_S0 myK_S0
Alias myPi0 pi0
ChargeConj myPi0  myPi0
##
Decay B0sig
  1.000     myD*-  K+               SVS ;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
