1.0000    myanti-D0  pi-         VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay myD*+
#
Decay myD0
1.000     myK_S0 pi+  pi- myPi0  PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay myanti-D0
#
Decay myK_S0
1.000     pi+  pi-  PHSP;
Enddecay
#
Decay myPi0
1.0000  gamma gamma    PHSP;
Enddecay
